Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:13.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,日後會成為給主上殿下\N呈上白瓷碗的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼 既然有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您先答應我保護好這孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:21.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我的子女 只有一個毓道已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要向我爹道歉 馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你居然還有女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:30.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下登基不知不覺二十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:33.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,趁此機會我要推薦世子冊封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:35.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這回要處決的對象 是光海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,江天已經開始活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做一個宗廟祭的祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我會奉御令製作祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:43.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道他是何人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:47.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是在恭嬪的茶杯裏下毒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.74,0:00:48.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然給母親下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:53.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是太祖大王盛著建國氣韻製作的\N珍貴的罈子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你要如性命般珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可以啊 王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:04.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你怎麼沒有接住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為何看我 是你沒接住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.85,0:01:31.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你為何連這個都抓不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:32.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:36.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難 難道你這是在怪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是說不是就成為不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:51.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,醉酒後都不會走道的王兄\N讓你進宗廟祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:01:59.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你要如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒 琿兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:14.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒 琿兒 你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:18.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說了是我的錯 因此也要由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:22.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這是瘋了嗎 你真的要向父王稟報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒 琿兒等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,琿兒 琿兒等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這就不對了 你要想清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想得越多 越會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:44.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因此對王兄的埋怨也會越大\N我不想那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這是真打算要使我難堪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:54.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是父王如性命般珍惜的罈子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王肯定會重罰的 你怎能如實稟報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再加上 我還沒有醒酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以這副樣子怎能拜見父王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:07.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此怕父王的人\N怎能讓事情發生到這個地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-當初你就\N-閉嘴 我不需要你來教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:16.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,父王如性命般珍惜的\N你為何放在那上面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你以為你能平安無事嗎\N好 那我們就走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,仁嬪在裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:48.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那我們下次再來吧 琿兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:18.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你們來了嗎 父王 既然王兄們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那麼小兒就退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有何事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有重要事相告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:53.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還在磨蹭什麼 有話快說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:00.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來臣妾還是先退下吧 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底有什麼話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是在嬪面前不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:14.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的 我說 今日祭陽所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來了乙檀製作的祭器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,於是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:39.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,能否用在宗廟祭 我想由父王過目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這不爭氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,寡人不是封你為副提調嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,決定也要你出 責任也要由你擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為何要煩寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你呢 你來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什 麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒 沒有 就寢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走 走吧 琿兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做得很好 編得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,差點做了信城的好事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如今連向父王如實相告的機會\N也錯失掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:29.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,該如何是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是啊 你應該感到害怕\N闖了這麼大的禍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我還真是擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所有的錯都應該由你來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可身為兄長 我豈能旁觀弟弟的危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-我也會幫你想想辦法\N-不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然說所有都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辦法也由我一個人想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:07:00.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好久不見 你怕責怪才沒有來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我很慚愧 娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我不會再因為冊封世子之事來責備你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:13.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下哪是那麼輕易決定的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,娘娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,現在才正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨晚光海君和臨海君拜見殿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定是祭陽所出了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你快去查看 到底是出了什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:35.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有何事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:39.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨晚祭陽所似乎出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這種話 我不是在你口中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,而是要在仁嬪娘娘那裏聽到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你讓我的臉面往哪擱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:48.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:54.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就想著毫無意義的乙檀\N眼耳都被蒙住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:58.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到底祭陽所發生何事 你快去查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個不是乙檀的祭器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:53.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來是有名良班家令郎\N到底有何事來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎的茶杯 修復成原有模樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道這種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這種事就要去找分院的陶瓷匠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:14.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就因為不能去找分院 才回來這的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:18.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,聽說這裏販賣明瓷器非常活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:21.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明那邊 沒有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:26.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這裏只交易的物品 不會交易人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:30.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,報酬會充分支付給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還是請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:44.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫火靈 日前在酒家見過一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:49.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您在找修補碎碗的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去找井兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:10:00.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 一有空就會修補碎碗\N有時連師父都認不出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙坦還有女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:10.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是和泰道哥一起在山上見到的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:15.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是說\N那個叫井兒的孩子那天也在山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去見一下破器匠 你要守好家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,破器匠大人的話 是不是火靈的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:27.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就是說能帶回火靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那也要看她的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,誰知道她願不願回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈肯定也想快點見到我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一定要帶回來 一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要好好守好家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:46.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可不要像上次似的 玩得連手都弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:50.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,放心吧 我不會離開家門一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:51.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:25.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼出來了 禁足令解開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是不是偷跑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹去火靈家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對了 你教我騎馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小心點騎 別害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,馬兒 要多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,握緊韁繩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:54.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,赤兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-井兒\N-快救我 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:02.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先看看大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:37.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,每次見面都這麼驚天動地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:58.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 怎麼是好啊 都摔壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:07.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道就沒有 贖回火靈的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底欠了多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這件事你就別再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:24.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我倆之間 何必呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下不是很愛惜 你的手藝的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,指不定哪一天 你就成了朗廳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別說這些沒用的\N還是想辦法贖回火靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,跪著幹什麼\N我都說了我是在等乙檀回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我爹是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:56.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要殺就殺我 要貶為奴我也一力承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:57.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求您放過我爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那天在山上是我要井兒逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要罰就罰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙坦到底什麼時候回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小女都說了 甘願領受處罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:17.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您為什麼死咬著我爹不放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我什麼時候說過怎麼著你爹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:27.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那好 只要我處罰你就可以了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:31.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 謝謝您 謝謝您 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼處罰都願意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:45.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人 那是自然 小女之罪豈是等閒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟敢擰大人您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:52.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還說謊要看到您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,必須斬下您的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:57.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不相信您是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,王子 真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:03.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還對您說出大不敬的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,何止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還為了就顫慄的您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然把自己的裙子 蓋住了您的玉體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:13.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,身體一暖 就不那麼難受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:26.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂 那個... 快住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我本人知道的很清楚 不用再用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要處罰與你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快閉上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還剩下兩下 快閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這就是處罰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪裏 怎麼會不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請快行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這就完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不如找井兒看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:56.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,算了吧 那種黃毛丫頭能知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:17:00.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:04.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:06.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 小女孩是放不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,非得挨那兩下彈指是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:18.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是那件事 我給您修復那件碎瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然是我打碎的 就交給我來修復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,俗話說有其父必有其女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你知道這是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,必定是貴重瓷器 這當然能猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這可不是你這黃毛丫頭可以修復的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:39.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 我雖然看起來有點毛毛躁躁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是修復瓷器卻很有兩下子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說不可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,修復了這個 你就成了犯了謀逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:51.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 不相信我您就直說了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:55.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不就是修復瓷器嗎\N有什麼大不了的 說什麼謀逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:59.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道還能大過 對您犯的大不敬之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,需要幾天之內完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的 有信心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,到時候您可不要被嚇到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,五天 給你五天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:26.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,足夠了 路上小心 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫你們好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:45.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然不知道他去了哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您不是說只要不讓他\N去找殿下就可以了嗎 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,既然出了宮 您就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你小子 還敢頂嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼不叫醒我 或者跟蹤他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你 你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,立刻去打探他都幹了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼還杵在這裏不動\N還不去康寧店守著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是光海出現\N你一定要給我阻止他見殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然出了宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:48.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您此行是不是為了 太祖大王壇之事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:53.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海來過這裏 他怎麼說\N說是我打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 莫非是您打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是我 是光海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,真的是光海君大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混帳 現在重要的不是這事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要尋根溯源的話 也只能怪教唆我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你就是罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:17.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說起我的本意\N倒更希望打碎祭器的人是乙坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給我粘上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:20.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:24.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此事都怪你 所以由你...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,由朗廳你來修復不是應該的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:35.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辦不到 你也配做朝鮮第一沙器匠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 太祖大人壇是何等貴重之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎是謀逆大罪 修復也是謀逆大罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,微臣實在不明白\N您為什麼非要讓微臣成為謀逆之臣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,碎瓷現在在誰手裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:57.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然是在光海手裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可光海君大人沒來分院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那 他還會去找誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這次是 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:11.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:20.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:26.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海去找乙檀 怎麼就成了機會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:30.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,宗廟祭時文武百官都會出席
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:37.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果到時指認打碎者是光海君大人\N修復者是乙檀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不可 萬萬不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是光海他...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:45.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一舉除掉光海君和乙坦的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您想要任之溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:52.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,光海可是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:59.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也是爭奪世子之位的 勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.16,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要做怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:17.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,相信我 等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:49.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:50.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:54.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是陶土塊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.07,0:23:04.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼沒有呢  應該是在這裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:07.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有那一塊就做不出來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以說為什麼要攬下那個活兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥 叫你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:15.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼不回家 還要在這裏嘮叨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:20.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這個性格真是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:25.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果是柳乙檀的事情 就不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:30.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是作為邊首 來找郎廳大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:36.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,祭陽所出了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:40.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有個碗消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:43.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,太祖大王的碗是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:46.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個不是消失了 而是弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.32,0:23:48.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是怎麼知道的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:50.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:01.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要給副提調光海君大人\N報告這件事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:06.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎這個的人 正是光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:13.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那光海君大人 會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:15.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,會出大事的 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:20.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以大人肯定會想著要復原那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:24.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.86,0:24:25.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.59,0:24:27.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那我就去找光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.43,0:24:29.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我幫他復原
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:34.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就會變成大逆罪人 難道你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:40.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,知道 可不能看著大人成為大逆罪人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:46.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你覺得他會找你幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:50.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,應該已經找別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:54.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有這一塊 就無法復原的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.22,0:24:56.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你真的就那麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.42,0:24:58.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:05.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你那麼吹捧的乙檀 你覺得會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.60,0:25:11.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 把這件事情交給了 柳乙坦是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.57,0:25:14.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那要等著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.98,0:25:19.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可 你的表情怎麼會那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:23.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道沒有找你 你覺得很難過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.32,0:25:26.15,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.15,0:25:33.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算大人下命令\N也絕對不能做那件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:47.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,瀝青和白礬粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.21,0:25:53.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:55.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不知道白帆粉末嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:56.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:01.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這個縫隙真是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:03.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道還要有白土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:05.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我沒做過這種
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.36,0:26:10.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井 井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.03,0:26:14.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈呢 沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.70,0:26:19.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這些都是什麼呀 怎麼會在這裏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:24.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是大人拿過來的 讓我弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:28.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.28,0:26:30.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-爹\N-大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.49,0:26:33.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 你沒事嗎 怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.42,0:26:36.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥幫我扶他去屋裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.83,0:26:42.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 這可怎麼辦好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.60,0:26:45.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,居然會把那個罈子弄碎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.17,0:26:47.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那是什麼罈子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.74,0:26:53.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人說了什麼 是叫你黏那個的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.51,0:26:57.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是啊 大人說不行 是我硬搶過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:03.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他說粘了這個會成為大逆罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:05.62,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,粘個碗算什麼 怎麼會是大逆罪人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.45,0:27:08.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.56,0:27:10.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.39,0:27:12.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,現在開始好好聽清楚我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.06,0:27:20.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打碎這個罈子\N還要黏上這個罈子的 都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.67,0:27:21.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:23.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.60,0:27:24.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳井
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.44,0:27:26.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.64,0:27:28.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,回去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.48,0:27:30.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,泰道你也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.27,0:27:57.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只要確認一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.84,0:27:59.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.65,0:28:08.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.58,0:28:12.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.94,0:29:39.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.27,0:30:44.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個不要拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.57,0:30:49.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,求你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.34,0:30:53.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.75,0:30:57.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命呀 有山賊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.95,0:30:59.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.29,0:31:08.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 爹您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:12.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會跟到這裏來 還不快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:15.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不要 我好害怕呀 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:18.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如果我自己遇到山賊可怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:26.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.22,0:31:38.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,腿好痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.10,0:31:44.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,呸嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.20,0:31:45.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,過了這個山就好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.67,0:31:47.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.50,0:31:48.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要不要我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.24,0:31:49.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好呀 背我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.70,0:31:54.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 背你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.28,0:32:06.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀的包裏裏有破碎的罈子是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.95,0:32:08.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.42,0:32:12.09,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,難道說拿著那些碎片半夜逃跑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:13.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.50,0:32:20.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要保管破碎的罈子 最先需要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.90,0:32:22.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:24.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到相同的泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如此
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.77,0:32:29.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,他是去尋找泥土了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.81,0:32:36.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀師父他 真的負責了此事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.99,0:32:45.86,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的才能 很快便會成為你的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.25,0:33:10.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.08,0:33:13.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是乙檀 請受我一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.36,0:33:22.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,幹嘛傻站著 還不行禮
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.93,0:33:24.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是我的閨女
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.40,0:33:25.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請受她一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.47,0:33:34.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我叫作井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.26,0:33:50.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.46,0:33:51.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,趕緊給我拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.92,0:33:53.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.19,0:34:22.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,支離破碎了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.12,0:34:26.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這麼寶貝的東西怎麼落得這幅田地
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.06,0:34:27.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只要幫忙找到泥土 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:30.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就你這個犯了謀反罪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.46,0:34:34.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我會悄然回去 不會給師父添亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:37.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.07,0:34:39.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.27,0:34:41.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還請師父暫時替我照顧著
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:43.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.31,0:34:45.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是我遭遇不測
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.51,0:34:48.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒就托付給你了 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:50.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.28,0:34:51.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是我打碎的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.75,0:34:55.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是爹您為什麼會遭遇不測呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.79,0:34:58.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 求您了 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.09,0:35:00.56,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:02.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我可以做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.40,0:35:06.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我一定會黏的好好的 任誰都看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.43,0:35:08.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.10,0:35:12.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你說你叫井兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.41,0:35:15.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.99,0:35:32.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做成太祖大王罈子的泥土\N是金剛山的凍土
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.06,0:35:37.63,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這些都是裝泥土的罈子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:39.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你給找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.83,0:35:42.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在這麼多泥土中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.04,0:35:44.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎麼 你打算放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.60,0:35:46.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.44,0:35:48.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:55.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,要是找到了 就給我拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.72,0:35:58.19,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.56,0:36:11.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,上哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.87,0:36:14.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.70,0:36:15.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,在這兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.44,0:36:16.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.00,0:36:22.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是井兒的四柱八字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.14,0:36:24.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您怎麼還有這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.98,0:36:26.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.45,0:36:30.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算你再怎麼想阻止也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.12,0:36:31.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.59,0:36:34.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這傢伙的八字這麼明擺著寫著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.52,0:36:36.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這都是那孩子的命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.72,0:36:37.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你的業報
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.82,0:36:39.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.66,0:36:42.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您覺得井兒真的能找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.96,0:36:44.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.06,0:36:45.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然找不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.17,0:36:47.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有的泥土上哪兒找去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.37,0:36:51.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那您還讓她去找您都不信的\N金剛山凍土嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.04,0:36:55.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這當爹的人\N怎麼就這麼不懂自個兒閨女的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.44,0:37:00.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,腦門上明擺著寫著 頑固不化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.58,0:37:04.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這孩子可不是讓她止步就能止步的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.25,0:37:07.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,得讓她自己會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.40,0:37:21.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還在找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:28.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,換個短命的 早就歸西了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:31.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就算我再怎麼找都沒有相同的泥土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.41,0:37:33.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那若是如此你就如實相告便好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.25,0:37:34.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,瞎磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.72,0:37:37.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是沒有相同的泥土就要做出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.39,0:37:42.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我現在正在將各種泥土混合著做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.06,0:37:42.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.79,0:37:44.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.66,0:37:50.50,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井 井 井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:55.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.27,0:37:57.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,做出來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.18,0:38:05.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:07.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.01,0:38:08.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這孩子放在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.85,0:38:10.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.59,0:38:22.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快請進
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:26.83,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.83,0:38:28.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,沒見到她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.30,0:38:30.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,男子漢大丈夫不想點大事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.14,0:38:32.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就只知道井兒井兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.44,0:38:34.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給我來一罈子米酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:36.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,去拿米酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.41,0:38:41.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.88,0:38:44.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你也幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.82,0:38:45.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.55,0:38:47.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我們泰道這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:50.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,讓他當個捕卒也好 還勞煩你幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:52.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙說的什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:56.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎喲 聽說你們家\N連光海君大人都會進出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:01.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:03.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來得去找大人一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.21,0:39:08.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.51,0:39:12.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我是來見光海君大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:14.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還不給我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.55,0:39:17.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我說 只要幫忙傳句話就好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:18.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,為什麼不通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.95,0:39:20.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這不是泰道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.42,0:39:21.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼來這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.89,0:39:23.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,武官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.84,0:39:36.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.30,0:39:40.24,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,太祖大王的罈子不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.81,0:39:46.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哦 那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.58,0:39:51.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,暫時放在了我經常進出的熟人那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.62,0:39:54.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很快就會放回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.96,0:40:00.43,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.79,0:40:03.73,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,雖然不知大人作何想法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:07.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人覺得大人很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.77,0:40:11.07,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以大人若然覺得小人能有所幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.07,0:40:14.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就請放心告訴小人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.37,0:40:16.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不管是如何危險之事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:18.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人都會為了大人去做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.78,0:40:20.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你能如此說
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.61,0:40:22.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.79,0:40:31.26,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.73,0:40:36.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是信不過小人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.60,0:40:38.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.64,0:40:45.94,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有一位名叫柳乙檀的人求見
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:46.31,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.31,0:40:47.04,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:48.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:51.45,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,帶他 帶他來此處
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.45,0:40:53.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.38,0:40:57.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,今天能否請你先迴避一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.32,0:40:59.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我有要事和乙檀商量
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.35,0:41:02.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.71,0:41:21.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.17,0:41:22.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.48,0:41:26.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你小子就在這裏等著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:28.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.86,0:41:38.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,聽說那野豬就是你小子抓到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:40.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊 是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.99,0:41:42.46,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等人的這會功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.46,0:41:44.66,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就來看看你小子的射箭水平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.03,0:41:45.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.76,0:42:16.23,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,蒙上他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.92,0:42:43.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.86,0:42:50.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人存了逆心 打碎了太祖大王的罈子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:53.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所以 特來呈秉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.30,0:42:54.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你現在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.14,0:42:56.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說的是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.97,0:43:01.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人的閨女連累到大人之事死不足惜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.38,0:43:02.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.94,0:43:07.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,她還是個不知天高地厚的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.35,0:43:09.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還請您
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.82,0:43:12.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,饒她一命
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:14.22,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你起來
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.22,0:43:14.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.96,0:43:19.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你起來 要求情的人反而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.83,0:43:22.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個罈子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:24.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,一開始就是打碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.87,0:43:25.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.97,0:43:30.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我聽說井兒對打碎的器皿\N有獨到的見解
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.74,0:43:32.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,心存僥倖就...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.57,0:43:34.41,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若是你能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.41,0:43:36.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說不定能夠成功\N出於這樣的希望我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.98,0:43:40.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我現在就會告訴殿下事實的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.28,0:43:42.48,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,讓所有的事情回到原點
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.48,0:43:43.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.58,0:43:45.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不用了 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.52,0:43:48.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,若然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.72,0:43:52.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人定會處於困境 這不用想便知
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.13,0:43:55.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人是小人的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.33,0:43:57.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.90,0:44:01.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,救命恩人 你是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:03.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.50,0:44:06.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,多虧了您的出生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.71,0:44:10.74,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小人才得以免去處刑 重新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.48,0:44:14.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可以稱之為救命恩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.88,0:44:20.65,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒 您就相信她一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.86,0:44:26.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不過 若事情有變
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.36,0:44:30.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,所有責任就請推卸到小人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.67,0:44:38.27,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就請保護... 井兒那孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.78,0:44:45.25,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人如今...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.98,0:44:48.92,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,竟然都明目張膽的出入王宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.92,0:44:51.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,說兩位之間有要緊事相談
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.22,0:44:53.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,如被趕走搬出了門
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.69,0:44:55.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還會是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.89,0:44:59.93,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把碗復原 救大人與危難之中
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.93,0:45:03.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,然後要這郎廳之位 這不明擺著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.33,0:45:05.80,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.17,0:45:08.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,柳乙檀前輩總不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.00,0:45:10.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你到底是單純還是缺根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:16.81,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀為何要拼上性命 幫助光海君大人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.54,0:45:21.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,承擔著大逆罪人的風險\N非要復原的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.05,0:45:24.89,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,還能是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.45,0:45:30.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這身手 只在後山狩獵真是太委屈了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.39,0:45:33.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,有你這使弓箭的身手\N不管內禁衛還是兼司僕
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.33,0:45:35.90,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,想進哪個都可以 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.90,0:45:38.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您過獎了 我還有許多不足
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.83,0:45:41.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說了 我這個兼司樸長保證了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.24,0:45:45.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不僅是弓箭 刀法也非常了得
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.91,0:45:48.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這點我能保證
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.68,0:45:54.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等碗做完了 就帶到銅器店街道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.72,0:45:57.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,四天後的未時
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.40,0:46:11.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,杯子漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.87,0:46:13.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,漏了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.43,0:46:15.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.27,0:46:18.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是故意摔碎並黏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.57,0:46:22.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我還真沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.14,0:46:24.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我用了鴿子白
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.45,0:46:28.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是說雞蛋白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.85,0:46:32.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,把雞子白與黏著劑攪拌在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.15,0:46:35.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就能讓人察覺不到這是黏上的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.19,0:46:39.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可一倒熱水進去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.76,0:46:43.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,就會像這樣雞子白融化掉從而漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.16,0:46:46.00,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,然後就可以看到裂痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.00,0:46:48.20,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那麼您認為柳乙檀此人...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.94,0:46:51.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也會用雞子白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.51,0:46:52.97,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.44,0:46:59.21,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,比起稱呼為前輩 要好聽多了 毓道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.30,0:47:21.60,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來 製作泥巴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.97,0:47:22.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.70,0:47:24.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不得有黏著劑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.54,0:47:26.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.01,0:47:27.84,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,接著 嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.71,0:47:37.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.11,0:48:39.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹 我弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.84,0:49:08.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小丫頭 費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.88,0:49:11.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,小小年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.91,0:50:53.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.75,0:50:57.05,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,昨夜太暗 罈子看起來比較奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.78,0:50:59.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,可這起來一看 完全看不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.19,0:51:04.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,當然 理應如此
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.86,0:51:07.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,也不看看是誰的手藝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.75,0:51:37.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你能把他們引開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.24,0:51:57.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.98,0:51:59.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先跑了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:05.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.06,0:52:18.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.47,0:52:23.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哎呦 不好意思啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.30,0:52:24.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臭...臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.61,0:52:29.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,抓住他 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.75,0:52:32.85,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.58,0:52:34.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.39,0:52:45.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來人啊 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.33,0:52:47.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,-抓住他\N-快抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.53,0:52:50.10,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,抓住他 抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.93,0:52:53.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是罪人 是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.48,0:53:02.58,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,火靈
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.25,0:53:07.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.28,0:53:11.02,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.49,0:53:13.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:15.79,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.89,0:53:17.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.88,0:53:36.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是誰呀 砸碎這個的人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.44,0:53:40.38,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這可是明國使臣帶來的珍貴瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.75,0:53:43.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我要聯繫使臣館 請兩位稍後
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.32,0:53:45.52,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,誰都不許走
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.89,0:53:47.35,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看來不在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.72,0:53:48.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:12.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,等一下 他們還在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.78,0:54:14.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.98,0:54:17.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.61,0:54:45.71,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.39,0:55:03.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那個 復原了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.70,0:55:05.53,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,啊是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.34,0:55:15.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.15,0:55:28.29,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你這麼辛苦 想要什麼 我給你買
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.86,0:55:31.96,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不 不走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.16,0:55:36.36,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.54,0:55:47.01,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,來隨便挑
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.98,0:55:55.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,給泰道買也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.55,0:55:59.49,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你哥也為了幫你吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.59,0:56:01.69,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.69,0:56:04.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,哥哥他什麼忙也沒有幫
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.83,0:56:10.13,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我爹也沒有幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.60,0:56:15.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,只有我 跟此事有關的只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.84,0:56:22.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這樣我該做的也做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.65,0:56:30.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,以後大人跟我不再相見
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.52,0:56:35.82,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,爹跟我才能平安
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.76,0:56:41.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您多多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.00,0:56:49.77,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您照顧好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.57,0:57:29.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.61,0:57:34.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說了我不會再回師父那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.28,0:57:36.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那井兒怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.75,0:57:39.32,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒她很想你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.46,0:57:47.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,很想我 有多想
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.06,0:57:55.47,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,因為太想我 晚上睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.94,0:57:59.14,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,看著月亮哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.08,0:58:03.91,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,井兒就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.64,0:58:05.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我帶她來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.75,0:58:07.95,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你還是如此執著 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.78,0:58:14.55,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 我怕我會恨井兒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.76,0:58:20.06,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,外面安靜了 慢走不送
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.07,0:58:35.11,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,這真的是你 井兒你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.30,0:58:56.40,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.86,0:59:01.17,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,夜深了 大人為何來此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.17,0:59:03.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,明天就是宗廟祭
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.37,0:59:05.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我來做最後的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.57,0:59:08.51,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臣亦如此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.51,0:59:09.98,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,那就慢慢檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.34,0:59:12.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.56,0:59:25.03,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,怎會如此
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.13,0:59:28.33,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,簡直完美無缺
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.76,0:59:56.59,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,別做了 絕對不成
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.89,1:00:00.99,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,您是說
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.73,1:00:04.30,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我去確認過
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.30,1:00:06.87,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,簡直一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.34,1:00:14.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 殿下發問大人只要沈默就好
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.57,1:00:16.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,都說了別做了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.78,1:00:20.08,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,乙檀那傢伙 簡直就是神之手 神之手
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.45,1:00:24.12,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人 就算他再怎麼技藝卓群
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.12,1:00:27.42,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,打破罈子是事實
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.42,1:00:30.72,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,臣有辦法證明
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.60,1:00:37.70,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.37,1:00:43.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,你還有臉來見我
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.77,1:00:49.44,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫你打聽祭陽所發生何事\N你要拖到幾時
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:52.75,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,我定會在殿下面前參上一本
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.75,1:00:55.68,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,叫殿下把你分院郎廳革職查辦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.68,1:00:57.88,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,宗廟祭結束後
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.35,1:01:03.76,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大人如此對我 定會後悔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.33,1:01:12.57,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,請您看清楚光海君大人和乙檀的下場
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.34,1:01:19.54,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,再來練習一次祭祀禮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.84,1:01:25.78,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,先把太祖大王的罈子放上去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.78,1:01:27.61,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.82,1:01:32.39,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,主上殿下駕到
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.60,1:01:49.64,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,祭祀前\N寡人親自過來看看是否一切準備妥當
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.57,1:01:57.34,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大膽 這麼珍貴的東西\N你竟敢赤手拿著
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.27,1:02:19.37,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,大膽
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.37,1:02:22.67,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,殿下 請殿下息怒
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.67,1:02:28.18,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,此太祖大王的罈子摔碎了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.18,1:02:29.28,Default Drama2,,0,0,0,,摔碎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.54,1:02:59.01,Next2,,0,0,0,,*下集預告*
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.11,1:03:01.94,Next2,,0,0,0,,把他帶下去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.94,1:03:03.78,Next2,,0,0,0,,就上經一次 請網開一面
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.78,1:03:07.45,Next2,,0,0,0,,這是證明罈子曾經摔碎過的唯一辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.45,1:03:09.28,Next2,,0,0,0,,此次剷除對象是光海君
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.28,1:03:12.59,Next2,,0,0,0,,讓無辜之人蒙受不白之冤\N難道這就是殿下的王道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.59,1:03:14.42,Next2,,0,0,0,,給我住嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.42,1:03:15.16,Next2,,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.16,1:03:16.62,Next2,,0,0,0,,快回家去 快
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.62,1:03:19.93,Next2,,0,0,0,,把我爹放了 抓我
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.93,1:03:21.03,Next2,,0,0,0,,你去做個碗來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.03,1:03:22.50,Next2,,0,0,0,,我不會做碗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.50,1:03:25.07,Next2,,0,0,0,,定要重罰
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.07,1:03:27.27,Next2,,0,0,0,,她跟我一樣 一出生就沒了娘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.27,1:03:28.74,Next2,,0,0,0,,我娘生下我後就...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.74,1:03:30.57,Next2,,0,0,0,,本就該斬草除根
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.57,1:03:32.41,Next2,,0,0,0,,寡人會再思量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.75,comment2,,0,0,0,,第3回
